  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the <strong>Running Riot</strong> gauntlet, where you'll engage in <strong>heart-pounding</strong> combat against enemies trying to take you down! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/0d36bbfa10c62720a587a2b99dc8de2f.poster.avif?t=1754064945\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/0d36bbfa10c62720a587a2b99dc8de2f.webm?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/0d36bbfa10c62720a587a2b99dc8de2f.mp4?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Devastating Abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/f40f33625fc47f7f438c54b77b8bbaa1.poster.avif?t=1754064945\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/f40f33625fc47f7f438c54b77b8bbaa1.webm?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/f40f33625fc47f7f438c54b77b8bbaa1.mp4?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're no pushover. You'll gain Upgrades as you level up, making your abilities stronger. Your choices will determine whether victory will be yours!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/7ea8a8b2437fb467c9ac005177a98acf.poster.avif?t=1754064945\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/7ea8a8b2437fb467c9ac005177a98acf.webm?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/7ea8a8b2437fb467c9ac005177a98acf.mp4?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each class comes with its own set of unique abilities, upgrades, and meta-progression perks. Classes present new playstyles to master and new opportunities to nail that <strong>perfect run</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Score Attack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/013a8deb43a1c0fd88ccf4e953cd6662.poster.avif?t=1754064945\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/013a8deb43a1c0fd88ccf4e953cd6662.webm?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/013a8deb43a1c0fd88ccf4e953cd6662.mp4?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run grants you Running Riot <strong>Tickets </strong>based on how high you score. Use those tickets to buy perks and get even higher scores! So keep on <i>running</i>, keep on <i>rioting</i>, and you'll keep on finding more explosive ways to play! Don't forget to see how you rank amongst other players.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the <strong>Running Riot</strong> gauntlet, where you'll engage in <strong>heart-pounding</strong> combat against enemies trying to take you down! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/0d36bbfa10c62720a587a2b99dc8de2f.poster.avif?t=1754064945\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/0d36bbfa10c62720a587a2b99dc8de2f.webm?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/0d36bbfa10c62720a587a2b99dc8de2f.mp4?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Devastating Abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/f40f33625fc47f7f438c54b77b8bbaa1.poster.avif?t=1754064945\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/f40f33625fc47f7f438c54b77b8bbaa1.webm?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/f40f33625fc47f7f438c54b77b8bbaa1.mp4?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're no pushover. You'll gain Upgrades as you level up, making your abilities stronger. Your choices will determine whether victory will be yours!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/7ea8a8b2437fb467c9ac005177a98acf.poster.avif?t=1754064945\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/7ea8a8b2437fb467c9ac005177a98acf.webm?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/7ea8a8b2437fb467c9ac005177a98acf.mp4?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each class comes with its own set of unique abilities, upgrades, and meta-progression perks. Classes present new playstyles to master and new opportunities to nail that <strong>perfect run</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Score Attack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/013a8deb43a1c0fd88ccf4e953cd6662.poster.avif?t=1754064945\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/013a8deb43a1c0fd88ccf4e953cd6662.webm?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284000/extras/013a8deb43a1c0fd88ccf4e953cd6662.mp4?t=1754064945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run grants you Running Riot <strong>Tickets </strong>based on how high you score. Use those tickets to buy perks and get even higher scores! So keep on <i>running</i>, keep on <i>rioting</i>, and you'll keep on finding more explosive ways to play! Don't forget to see how you rank amongst other players.</p>",
